articles.title: Lionel Messi injured but Angel Di Maria stars as Paris Saint-Germain beat Lille - European round-up - Sky Sports
articles.description: Angel Di Maria set up the first goal and scored the winner to give Paris Saint-Germain a 2-1 win against Lille in Ligue 1 after Lionel Messi limped off injured.
